#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:1
msgid "Contributing to IOU Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:3
msgid ""
"The IOU Architecture Framework is an open-source project published under the "
"[European Union Public Licence v1.2 (EUPL-1.2)]{1}. Contributions of any "
"kind — documentation improvements, bug reports, feature suggestions, or code "
"— are welcome from everyone."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:10
msgid "Code of Conduct"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:12
msgid ""
"This project adheres to the principles of the [Contributor Covenant Code of "
"Conduct]{1}. By participating you agree to uphold these principles:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:16
msgid ""
"**Be respectful and inclusive.** Treat all participants with dignity "
"regardless of background, experience level, gender, ethnicity, religion, or "
"nationality."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:18
msgid ""
"**Assume good faith.** Interpret ambiguous contributions charitably and ask "
"for clarification before escalating concerns."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:20
msgid ""
"**Be constructive.** Feedback should focus on the work, not the person. "
"Offer concrete suggestions rather than criticism alone."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:22
msgid ""
"**Respect the scope.** Keep discussions on-topic for the project. Off-topic, "
"harassing, or abusive behaviour will not be tolerated."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:25
msgid ""
"Violations can be reported confidentially to [steven.gort@ictu.nl]{1}. All "
"reports will be handled with discretion and care."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:30
msgid "Repositories"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/contributing%5Cindex.md:32
msgid ""
"Each component of the IOU Architecture ecosystem lives in its own repository "
"on the [open-regels.nl GitLab instance]{1}."
msgstr ""

